{{For|aspects of ritual slaughter governed by religious law|shechita|dhabiha}}
[[File:Legal requirements for ritual slaughter in Europe 2018.png|350px|thumb|Legal requirements for ritual slaughter in [[Europe]] 2018:
{{Legend|#FF0000|Stunning not required}}
{{Legend|#7CFC00|Post-cut stunning required}}
